item.title: Is the Imperial stereotype true?
item.author: Faye Hemsley,
item.description: So it’s two weeks in, and things aren’t going as you planned. It isn’t exactly how it was sold to you. Sure, you’ve been out most nights, met a million people you can’t remember, been a bit of a tourist and burnt a few meals. But you’ve also missed more 9am lectures than you made it to, piled up a …
